name: test 875
description: Last year we took the Phase franchise to the next level with the Phase BOA Pro, and this year we're continuing the progression with a Step On model. We added top-of-the-line tech to the simple, skate-inspired upper, starting with the BOA Fit System paired with our patent-pending SUPERLOCK heel harness to eliminate heel slip and deliver a more responsive ride. We also fitted it with our R3 liner with PrimaLoft insulation, our warmest and most responsive ever. Simply put, the Phase Boa Pro Step On is one of our most advanced boots ever^PRODUCT FEATURES: Step On[R] Outsole^Dual BOA[R] Fit System with H4 Coiler Tongue Dial and Internal Ankle Harness Controlled By Remote BOA[R] Dial^PrimaLoft[R] insulation^Response Liner III^Molded IMPACT-ALG Insole^BOA[R] Silver SS Laces^FLEX RATING 5/10

name: test 876
description: We designed the brand-new Premier Hybrid with input from the team, combining traditional lacing with our new, patent-pending SUPERLOCK heel harness, controlled by the BOA Fit System. This hybrid setup allows for great flexibility while maintaining that vital heel hold and responsiveness. Kitted out with our premium R2 liner, UNILITET outsole and molded IMPACT-ALGT insole, the Premier Hybrid is a perfect addition to the DC boot lineup^PRODUCT FEATURES: Traditional lacing and Internal Ankle Harness Controlled By Remote BOA[R] Dial^Contact UniLite[TM] Rubber Outsole^Response Liner III^PrimaLoft[R] insulation^Molded IMPACT-ALG Insole^Wrap Lock Hardware^Lacing Leverage^FLEX RATING 6/10

name: test 877
description: Taking inspiration from our rich skate footwear DNA, we refreshed the upper of the Control Boot for Winter '24.A tried-and-true, all-mountain boot, the Control is packed with top-of-the-line riding features like the industry-leading Dual Zone BOA Fit System. On the inside, we fitted it with our premium R2 liner with a 360 power strap. Our eco-friendly and ultra-comfy molded IMPACT-ALG insoles combine with the grippy UniliteT outsole to provide enhanced board feel at each and every turn^PRODUCT FEATURES: BOA[R] Fit System with H4 Coiler Dial and Zonal Closure Contact^UniLite[TM] Rubber Outsole^Response Liner II^Molded IMPACT-ALG Insole^Internal Ankle Harness^Articulated Construction^FLEX RATING 4/10

name: test 879
description: We put the team-favorite Judge Boot through the ringer year after year - testing, tweaking, and always making improvements with input from our riders. We added the eco-friendly and ultra-comfy molded IMPACT-ALGT insole for added comfort and better heel hold. The Judge also features our most advanced R3 liner-with PrimaLoft insulation and Aerotech ventilation to maintain the perfect foot temperature in any conditions. The Vibram outsole keeps the boot grippy yet light, while the Dual Zone BOA Fit System delivers a micro-adjustable, precision fit, engineered to perform in the toughest conditions. The Judge Boot really is designed (from top to bottom) to handle any mountain (from top to bottom)^PRODUCT FEATURES: Dual BOA[R] Fit System With H4 Coiler Dial^Vibram[R] Outsole^Response Liner III^Molded IMPACT-ALG^PrimaLoft[R] insulation^Internal Ankle Harness^Aerotech Ventilation System^BOA[R] Black SS Laces^FLEX RATING 6/10

name: test 880
description: The team-favorite Judge Step On combines DC's top-of-the-line boot tech with the convenience and performance of Burton's Step On interface. Since we're always focused on performance, the Judge features our most advanced R3 liner-with PrimaLoft insulation and Aerotech ventilation to maintain the perfect foot temperature in any conditions. We also added the eco-friendly and ultra-comfy molded IMPACT-ALGT insole for added comfort and better heel hold. The Dual Zone BOA Fit System provides a precision fit, so you can step on and ride in a matter of seconds^PRODUCT FEATURES: Step On[R] Outsole^Dual BOA[R] Fit System With H4 Coiler Dial^Response Liner III^Molded IMPACT-ALG Insole^PrimaLoft[R] insulation^Internal Ankle Harness^Aerotech Ventilation System^BOA[R] Black TX3 Laces^FLEX RATING 6/10

name: test 881
description: An OG style from 2001, the Phantom represented the best snow tech of the day, but we modernized it with top-of-the-line features for today's rider. Our ultra-responsive R3 liner is built with PrimaLoft insulation and the Aerotech ventilation system to maintain the perfect foot temperature in any conditions. The molded IMPACT-ALGT insole isn't just eco-friendly, it also provides perfect cushioning and heel hold. And on the outside we added the Dual Zone BOA Fit System which delivers a micro-adjustable, precision fit, engineered to perform in the toughest conditions. Today's Phantom is dripping in DC Snow heritage and ready to perform on the mountain. No wonder it's a favorite of so many of DC's team riders^PRODUCT FEATURES: Dual BOA[R] Fit System with Multi-color H4 Coiler Dials^Vibram[R] Outsole^Response Liner III^PrimaLoft[R] insulation^Aerotech Ventilation System^Molded IMPACT-ALG Insole^Internal Ankle Harness^Leather Tongue Overlay^BOA[R] Silver SS Laces^FLEX RATING 8/10

name: test 882
description: A longtime DC favorite, the Phase is a classic DC style with modern upgrades. With the same skate-inspired upper, the Phase is now equipped with the intuitive BOA Fit System which delivers a micro-adjustable, precision fit, engineered to perform in the toughest conditions. With an unbeatable price point and performance-focused tech features like IMPACT-ALGT insoles and UniliteT outsoles, the Phase BOA redefines what a simple, affordable boot can do on the mountain^PRODUCT FEATURES: BOA[R] Fit System with H4 Coiler^Foundation UniLite[TM] Outsole^Response Liner I^IMPACT-ALG Insole^BOA[R] Silver SS Laces^FLEX RATING 4/10

name: test 883
description: A longtime DC favorite, we once again upgraded the Phase BOA Pro to make it one of our top performing boots. This year we added our premium R3 liner with PrimaLoft insulation for our warmest and most technical fit. We also paired the BOA Fit System with our patent-pending SUPERLOCK heel harness to eliminate heel slip and deliver a more responsive ride. The Phase BOA Pro mixes skate-inspired simplicity with top-line tech features to conquer the most technical riding in the harshest winter conditions^PRODUCT FEATURES: Dual BOA[R] Fit System with H4 Coiler Tongue Dial and Internal Ankle Harness Controlled By Remote BOA[R] Dial^PrimaLoft[R] insulation^Contact UniLite[TM] Rubber Outsole^Response Liner III^Molded IMPACT-ALG Insole^BOA[R] Silver SS Laces FLEX RATING 5/10
